lore: Most blessed of all their kind, the Enlightened see the skeins of fate through communion with Tzeentch. They surge to battle atop daemonic Discs, their divining spears humming as they sense their predestined prey, their fatecaster greatbows launching ensorcelled arrows from ectoplasmic strings with lethal effect.
